org.afplib.afplib

Interface TileSize

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TileSizeImpl

    public interface TileSize
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Tile Size'.

    The following features are supported:

    • THSIZE
    • TVSIZE
    • RELRES

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getTileSize()
